						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 60 <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> for burning a light during services in the temple of Ūrbāgaṅkoṇḍaruḷiya-Nāyanar at Iṟaiyānaraiyūr <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Śōḻakēraḷa-chaturvēdimaṅgalam by a lady by name Māśaṟuśōdi Śāṉi wife of Āritaṉ Śaṅkaranārāyaṇaṉ Śrīkrishṇa-Bhaṭṭaṉ. A <hi rend="italic">Śivabrāhmaṇa</hi> of the temple was entrusted with the amount for this purpose.</p>						

						</summary>
